The paper discusses challenges related to networking, management, and resource modeling in federating Edge deployments. These topics are closely related to Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Networked and Distributed Systems (cs.NI), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Architecture (cs.AR). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
